united families in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI testify before Allah that no servant dies bearing witness there is no God but Allah and Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah and then does what is right, except that he will find his way\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34651,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/06\/all-paradise-but-stray-camels\/","url_meta":{"origin":37522,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: All enter Paradise but those who stray like camels","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, you will all surely enter Paradise except one who refuses and wanders away from Allah like a stray camel.\u201d It was said, \u201cWho would refuse to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11817,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/do-not-get-angry-enter-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":37522,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Do not get angry,  you will enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me about a deed that will admit me into Paradise.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not be angry and you will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304\u00a02353 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":268,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/14\/faith-truly-knows-allah-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":37522,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Whoever truly knows Allah enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever died truly knowing that there is no God but Allah will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 26 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645\u200f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/28\/all-jannah-but-refuse\/","url_meta":{"origin":37522,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: All Muslims enter Paradise but those who refuse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Everyone from my nation will enter Paradise but those who refuse.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, who will refuse?\" The Prophet said, \"Whoever obeys me enters Paradise, and whoever disobeys me has refused.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/believers-paradise-beautiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":37522,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Believers enter Paradise as young, beautiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people of Paradise will enter Paradise with smooth and hairless skin, kohl upon their eyes, at thirty or thirty-three years of age.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2545 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.a